---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="Raghavan Muthuregunathan is an AI search engineering leader focused on turning research into shipped systems."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="page">
			<section class="content">
				<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
				<h1>I build AI systems that move from research to production.</h1>
				<p>
					I am Raghavan Muthuregunathan, an engineering leader working at the intersection of
					search, information retrieval, machine learning, and applied generative AI. My work has
					focused on turning ambiguous user intent into useful product experiences: typeahead,
					spell correction, ranking, personalization, RAG, LLM-powered assistants, and search
					systems that have to operate at real-world scale.
				</p>
				<p>
					I currently lead Search AI work at LinkedIn. Earlier in my career, I worked on Microsoft
					Bing, where I built experience in large-scale search infrastructure and relevance. That
					combination shaped how I approach AI: start with the research, validate it with careful
					evaluation, and keep pushing until it becomes something reliable enough for people to use.
				</p>
				<p>
					I am especially interested in the practical frontier: retrieval quality, multilingual and
					translation-augmented generation, AI evaluation, trustworthy assistants, and the engineering
					discipline required to ship these systems into customer-facing workflows.
				</p>
				<div class="about-list">
					<h2>What I bring</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Deep search and information retrieval experience across Bing and LinkedIn.</li>
						<li>Hands-on applied AI work across ranking, personalization, RAG, and LLM systems.</li>
						<li>Engineering leadership for teams shipping production AI experiences.</li>
						<li>
							Community work with open and public-interest AI efforts, including GenAI Commons,
							Apache Solr, and disaster-management AI initiatives.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<p>
					This site is my home base for experiments, writing, and projects around practical frontier
					AI. You can find my code and experiments on
					<a href="https://github.com/Raghavan1988">GitHub</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
